  "description": "<p>We are looking for a Recruitment Consultant to join our growing team.</p><p>Job Responsibilities:</p><p>Source, screen, and interview candidates</p><p>Handle end-to-end recruitment process</p><p>Liaise with clients to understand hiring needs</p><p>Coordinate interviews and follow up with candidates</p><p>Maintain recruitment records and databases</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>Experience in recruitment or HR preferred</p><p>Good communication and interpersonal skills</p><p>Self-motivated and target-driven</p><p>Ability to work independently and as a team</p><p>Location: Singapore</p><p>Salary: Negotiable + Commission</p><p>Work Pass: Singaporean / PR / eligible pass holders<br /></p><p>INTERESTED CANDIDATES SEND DETAILED RESUME TO kcnea2023@gmail.com/WhatsApp 90383814<br /> </p><p>EALICENCE NO: 23C1613.</p>",
